== 普及 ==
現今，咖哩牛腩是香港[[茶餐廳|茶餐廳]]及[[港式快餐|港式快餐]]的常見菜式，在午餐及晚餐時段皆有供應<ref name="gotrip2016">{{cite news |title=6大連鎖店 咖哩牛腩飯比拼 邊間最好食? |url=https://www.gotrip.hk/261630/weekend_lifestyle/lifestyle/%e9%80%a3%e9%8e%96%e5%ba%97_%e5%92%96%e5%96%b1%e7%89%9b%e8%85%a9%e9%a3%af_%e6%af%94%e6%8b%bc/ |work=GOtrip |date=2016-11-10 |accessdate=2019-06-01 |archive-date=2019-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190601085843/https://www.gotrip.hk/261630/weekend_lifestyle/lifestyle/%e9%80%a3%e9%8e%96%e5%ba%97_%e5%92%96%e5%96%b1%e7%89%9b%e8%85%a9%e9%a3%af_%e6%af%94%e6%8b%bc/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。咖哩牛腩通常與[[白飯|白飯]]一起進食，如果兩者以同一碟上菜，便成為'''咖哩牛腩飯'''<ref name="et2017">{{cite news |title=咖哩牛腩飯 VS 焗豬扒飯　碟頭粉麵飯鈉含量龍虎榜 |url=https://topick.hket.com/article/1704252/%E5%92%96%E5%96%B1%E7%89%9B%E8%85%A9%E9%A3%AF%20VS%20%E7%84%97%E8%B1%AC%E6%89%92%E9%A3%AF%E3%80%80%E7%A2%9F%E9%A0%AD%E7%B2%89%E9%BA%B5%E9%A3%AF%E9%88%89%E5%90%AB%E9%87%8F%E9%BE%8D%E8%99%8E%E6%A6%9C |work=香港經濟日報 |date=2017-03-15 |accessdate=2019-06-01 |archive-date=2019-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190601085556/https://topick.hket.com/article/1704252/%E5%92%96%E5%96%B1%E7%89%9B%E8%85%A9%E9%A3%AF%20VS%20%E7%84%97%E8%B1%AC%E6%89%92%E9%A3%AF%E3%80%80%E7%A2%9F%E9%A0%AD%E7%B2%89%E9%BA%B5%E9%A3%AF%E9%88%89%E5%90%AB%E9%87%8F%E9%BE%8D%E8%99%8E%E6%A6%9C |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，香港還有一種稱為'''咖哩牛腩煲'''或'''咖哩牛腩鍋'''的[[煲仔菜|煲仔菜]]。

